    "---\n",
    "## 4. EfficientNet-B4 Model Architecture\n",
    "\n",
    "### Architecture Summary\n",
    "```\n",
    "Input (3×512×512)\n",
    "       ↓\n",
    "EfficientNet-B4 Backbone (ImageNet pretrained)\n",
    "  ├── Stem Conv (3×3, stride 2)\n",
    "  ├── MBConv Blocks × 32  [compound scaling: depth×1.8, width×1.4]\n",
    "  └── Head Conv (1×1) → Feature Maps (1792 channels)\n",
    "       ↓\n",
    "CBAM Attention Module\n",
    "  ├── Channel Attention (SE-Net style, reduction=16)\n",
    "  └── Spatial Attention (7×7 conv)\n",
    "       ↓\n",
    "Dual Global Pooling\n",
    "  ├── AdaptiveAvgPool2d(1) → [B, 1792]\n",
    "  └── AdaptiveMaxPool2d(1) → [B, 1792]\n",
    "       ↓  (concatenate)\n",
    "Classification Head [B, 3584]\n",
    "  ├── Linear(3584→512) + BN + ReLU + Dropout(0.4)\n",
    "  ├── Linear(512→256)  + BN + ReLU + Dropout(0.2)\n",
    "  └── Linear(256→5)\n",
    "       ↓\n",
    "Output Logits (5 classes)\n",
    "```"
   ]
  },
